RM_1.lemma_name: RM_1  : forall n:Z, RM n (Z_bnode n Z_leaf Z_leaf) Z_leaf.

rmax_7.lemma_name:
rmax_7  :
      forall q':Z,
        occ q' (Z_bnode n t1 t') -> occ q' (Z_bnode n t1 (Z_bnode p t2 t3)).

min_not_occ.lemma_name: min_not_occ  : forall (z:Z) (t:Z_btree), min z t -> ~ occ z t.

proof_steps: apply H in Hocc as Hlt.

not_right.lemma_name: not_right  : forall p:Z, p <= n -> ~ occ p t2.

proof_steps: destruct se as [Hst1 Hst2 Hmin Hmaj | Hst1 Hst2 Hmin Hmaj].

rmax_6.lemma_name:
rmax_6  :
      forall p0:Z, occ p0 (Z_bnode n t1 (Z_bnode p t2 t3)) -> p0 <= q.

go_right.lemma_name: go_right  : forall p:Z, occ p (Z_bnode n t1 t2) -> p > n -> occ p t2.

proof_steps: intros A B H1 H2 H3.

ex_imp_ex.lemma_name:
ex_imp_ex  :
 forall (A:Type)(P Q:A->Prop), (ex P)->(forall x:A, P x -> Q x)->(ex Q).

proof_steps: intros A P Q [y Hy] H.
intros P Q R H1 H2 HP.

le_mult_mult.lemma_name:
le_mult_mult  :
   forall a b c d:nat, a <= c -> b <= d -> a * b <= c * d.

proof_steps: intros a b c d Hac Hbd.

wp_o_head_c.lemma_name:
wp_o_head_c  :
 forall l1 l2:list par, wp l1 -> wp l2 -> wp (open :: l1 ++ close :: l2).

wp_o_tail_c.lemma_name:
wp_o_tail_c  :
 forall l1 l2:list par,
   wp l1 -> wp l2 -> wp (l1 ++ open :: l2 ++ close :: nil).

impredicative_le_n.lemma_name: impredicative_le_n  : forall n: nat, impredicative_le n n.

impredicative_sorted_to_sorted.lemma_name:
impredicative_sorted_to_sorted  :
    forall l, impredicative_sorted  l -> sorted  l.

proof_steps: intros x1 x2 l' H0 H1.
intros x1 x2 l' H0 H1.
intros x P Hnil Hsingle Hcons.

isorted2.lemma_name:
isorted2  :
    forall (x1 x2:A)(l':list A),
      R x1 x2 ->
      impredicative_sorted  (x2::l') ->
      impredicative_sorted  (x1::x2::l').

proof_steps: intros x1 x2 l' H1 H2.
